What Is Beamer?

Digital ads on
moving taxi screens
across Lagos.

Beamer operates a fleet of digital screens mounted on car rooftops. Your event ad plays every single minute across high-traffic routes in Lagos — reaching your audience where they already are. It's outdoor advertising that moves with the city.
